  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the efficacy of 8 mg of dexamethasone administered
      prior surgery, to reduce pain, postoperative nausea and vomiting and to improve vocal
      function after thyroidectomy for benign disease.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
